      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "14635-14687",
      "markText": "白嘉轩做出自轻自薄的口吻，又很恶毒地说：“咱们祖先一个铜子一个麻钱攒钱哩！人家凭卖尻子一夜就发财了嘛！”",
      "totalCount": 85,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27403434&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=14635&rangeEnd=14687",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e75323c071a224aae751829?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=14635&rangeEnd=14687"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27403434_5_380-402",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "380-402",
      "markText": "白嘉轩后来引以为豪壮的是一生里娶过七房女人。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27403434&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=380&rangeEnd=402",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e75323c071a224aae751829?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=380&rangeEnd=402"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "27403434_6_6356-6444",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6356-6444",
      "markText": "凡人们兴味十足甚至幸灾乐祸一番之后，很快就置自己刚刚说过的血淋淋的事例于脑后，又拼命去劳作去挣钱去迎接催命的鬼去了，在可能多买一亩土地再添一座房屋的机运到来的时候绝不错失良机。",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=27403434&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6356&rangeEnd=6444",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e75323c071a224aae751829?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6356&rangeEnd=6444"
    },
